metadata.description: The Genesis Collection is the beginning of this adventure, and they are the most valuable NFTs in our Multiverse. These NFTs are the true believers, the ones that stood up after the world was destroyed. These are the real #Survivors! Life Out is an utility NFT Project created on the Ethereum chain aiming to create a Multiverse that will reside in the web3 community.
